    </div>
    <div class="faq-container">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <h3>How can I track my order?</h3>
          <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>
            Once your order has been shipped, you will receive a confirmation
            email with a tracking number. You can use this number to track your
            package on our website under "Track Order" or directly through the
            courier's website.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <h3>Are all your products authentic?</h3>
          <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>
            Yes, we guarantee that all our products are 100% authentic. We
            source directly from official distributors and have partnerships
            with entertainment companies to ensure authenticity. Each product
            comes with a certificate of authenticity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <h3>What is your return policy?</h3>
          <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>
            We accept returns within 30 days of delivery for unused items in
            their original packaging. Please note that certain items like
            photocards and limited edition products may not be eligible for
            return unless they arrive damaged or defective.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <h3>Do you ship internationally?</h3>
          <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>
            Yes, we ship to most countries worldwide. Shipping times and costs
            vary depending on your location. We offer free shipping on orders
            over $150. Please note that customers are responsible for any
            customs fees or import taxes that may apply.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <h3>How do I join the VIP membership program?</h3>
          <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>
            You can join our VIP membership program by creating an account on
            our website and making a purchase. After your first purchase, you'll
            automatically be enrolled in our Bronze tier. As you make more
            purchases, you'll progress to Silver, Gold, and Platinum tiers, each
